Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 不要回头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 迈步出发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪是闪闪发光的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一步 都化为甘霖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更加自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要的东西就舍去 这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在无限广阔的心中蔓延开来哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于受伤时刻之外　看不见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.83,0:00:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若现在开始映入双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just Try-again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:01:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得强大 抓住机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 都要坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想绝对能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多遥远 都不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更能感觉到明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫战部渡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了打倒支配了在遥远天空上的星界山的多坏达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以第七星界为目标展开了冒险旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在身处的是有趣的热带第六星界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中了暗黑之剑成为魔界中人的武一郎师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在进发的途中到处追杀我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是,我们该怎样才能救出师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:02:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也会是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四十二话\N悲哀的玛达莉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要让我等到何时?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连把一个渡变成魔界份子也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的实力也只是如此吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算我多嘴了多坏达大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动不能顺利完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部是因为多余的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.77,0:02:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上一次战斗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你的儿子多余的插手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡才不是在下的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要推三推四的!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡、虎王、海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这三个人他们集合的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有想像以上的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.51,0:02:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要令渡变成魔界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便要让他们三人的心分离
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请交给我处理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也许会是我给你最后的命令了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早已觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧,多支达路!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡绝对要由我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷失在一个不得了的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有个傻瓜说这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说谁是傻瓜?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不过是建议而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的第六感真是不可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…你们不要这样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事便立刻吵架呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,去问问他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问这里是什么地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加拉桑森林呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么,去亚索加方向的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边正确吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓?什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子想想办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍法,蜘蛛丝呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你们只顾着吵架呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,你在笑什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快救我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多是时候放了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠着他们的不只是我的蜘蛛丝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的蜘蛛丝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,连我也被缠着了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要缠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,这次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒语)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还这么悠闲玩公仔吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是芭哈路大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说我在玩公仔?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是普通的公仔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是普通的公仔那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在加拉桑森林里粘上蜘蛛丝的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部能被我控制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样便能控制渡他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:06:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你所说的一样令他们的内心分离的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候就用黑龙角出击!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要失败啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于松脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,赶路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为何突然有不好的预感…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会发生什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的,你的预感才不会中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.33,0:06:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么?混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想打吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了…停手呀你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是普通的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫虎王的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样渡他们便在我的手中了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有一个不能控制,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能控制两个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要他们不和便轻而易举
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?手脚自然地动…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢打我的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能饶恕!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王,是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和自己的意识没关系,他在动呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌,控制不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我们非要这样不可?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才能感觉也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.64,0:07:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样看这个森林也有古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,虎王!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只有他能行动自如?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这时候古拿玛在的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想请问一下你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识一个在风暴中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出海捕渔之后行踪不明的男人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕渔失踪了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他当时应该是有一个二三岁的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道,我不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对渡他们干了什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只有我没事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已无路可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活该呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样?想讲话了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯讲的话,我便救你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要救我?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为最重要的事还未问你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脸上有什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡他们是中了死亡遥控魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是魔术吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要曾粘上一次那些蜘蛛丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使全部抓掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会留下一条用来遥控的丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此渡他们便变成那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我因为曾经是魔界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不被控制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔界的?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是魔界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要跟渡在一起?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我和渡是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子是我的新娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于海火子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不太喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大家一起的话很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快乐?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛达莉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫虎王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有朋友的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之,一天有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不会让你取渡的命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要这样拚命?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我和渡是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以,就算要了我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要保护渡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你快去救他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在他们被控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的会是自伤残杀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该怎么样做呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉你是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想渡他们被死亡遥控控制
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡要由我来救
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事怎么样也没所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样才能救到他们?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把放那条丝的蜘蛛杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣的事现在才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒语)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停…停手,海火子!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想停呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危…危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能饶恕你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,用魔神分胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏鬼丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么破烂魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?渡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦,我要和他打!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡遥控的蜘蛛便是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好…再打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大件事了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我会在夏鬼丸上的?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦,我怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,你清醒了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们发生了什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡遥控那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只差一步竟然先失手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪京芭、节芭利上了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要大意,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸,去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点啊,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们能看穿黑龙角的魔幻术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个才是真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:16:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话便用这个吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是正体了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必杀!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光龙剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要小看我们啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没有我的话便什么也做不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟敢说呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛虎变形!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气分胜负吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变形,飞龙!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞龙光击拳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪京芭!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,节芭利,雪京芭被击落了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为虎王收拾了那只蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以,我们才能自由吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但追根究底也是虎王你找我吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊,我什么时候!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,你们停一停呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛达莉斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛达莉斯,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.84,0:20:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让开!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不杀渡不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你杀我好朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快让开!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然连你也杀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟渡是好朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以,就算要了我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要保护渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛达莉斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛达莉斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛达莉斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背叛者吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.88,0:21:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛达莉斯,振作一点!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…很想要朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…我的朋友呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛达莉斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛达莉斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里便是那家伙的家?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.59,0:22:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 阴霾的天空里乌云渐渐散去 阳光透过云层照了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人仰望这天空的哪个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眩目的彩虹 即将出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:22:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注定出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.83,0:22:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.46,0:23:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着光线还没有消失的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.89,0:23:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待着明天的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.04,0:23:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.62,0:23:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熠熠生辉的彩虹彼岸里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.03,0:23:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹出了两个人未来的风

